  <summary>1/24/2002--Introduced.
Making Education, Nurturing, and Teaching Our Responsibility Act or the MENTOR Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to establish a limited (up to $20 an hour/$1040 annually) tax credit to an employer for wages paid to an employee mentoring a secondary school student through a quality mentoring program.</summary>
